data.description: Must see this home located in the peaceful Three Creeks community equipped with amenities to include walking trails, Chalk Ridge Park, volleyball courts, pavilions, and access to Lampasas River. It's perfect for those who love to enjoy the outdoors, with a covered front porch and back patio that are great for relaxing during any time of day. This home offers a 2 car garage, 5 bedrooms, 2-1/2 bathrooms,  large primary bedroom with a study/flex room, as well as a loft/ 2nd living area. The kitchen is perfect for hosting dinner parties and family gatherings,  it is truly a chef's dream, with stainless steel appliances & granite countertops. The primary bedroom is truly a showstopper, with an a study/reading nook and a primary suite bathroom that includes a walk-in shower, garden tub, double vanities,  massive closet, providing an oasis for homeowners to escape to after a long day. Upstairs, the home features 4 additional bedrooms, each with walk-in closets, providing plenty of space for a large family or guests. The loft/2nd living area is great for relaxation or as a space for kids to play.  Overall, this home is perfect for those who value both style and comfort in a peaceful and welcoming community.
